Package: anticlust
Type: Package
Title: Algorithms for the anticlustering problem
Version: 0.1.2
Author: Martin Papenberg
Maintainer: Martin Papenberg <martin.papenberg@hhu.de>
Description: `anticlust` is an R package to solve the anticlustering problem,
    i.e., assigning elements to groups in such a way that the groups are as
    similar as possible. The package also offers methods to solve 
    clustering problems. 
Encoding: UTF-8
License: Undecided
